{"tid":1634820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[謹記] 希望大家仲記得咩係Be Water 同 Be Humble","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:57.000Z","uid":2661,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef118affb033d90e0c4437c3ca4c996501e8efd7","tid":1634820,"uid":2661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:12:20.000Z","msg":"呢兩句說話係令到我地呢場運動得以持續超過100日<br />\n<br />\nBe water: <br />\n遍地開花 不戀戰 不打陣地 set完RB即走 裝修完即散水 <br />\n但尋日見灣仔一役仲有手足迷戀傘陣<br />\n要知道我地從來都係贏人數 陣地對峙我地武力上既差距會好蝕底 <br />\n手足一個都不可少<br />\n<br />\nBe humble:<br />\n唔應該因爲政見相反 就對鬧 對對家施以不必要既暴力 (警犬唔計 呢個對住落單狗要打大力d)<br />\n對於廢老藍絲既口舌之爭 慳返啖氣 無必要同佢地嘈<br />\n當然如果對家拎刀或對手足出手 傷害手足 歡迎自衛 （嫌尋日DC9打得唔夠 應該打到佢殘廢)<br />\n<br />\n記住驕兵必敗 只有保持 Be water Be humble 既心態 呢場運動先可以持續落去 同爭取更多人支持<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"3ca3ea9446ed2538f2497b7fc6f8d89fdce16eae","tid":1634820,"uid":2661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"12eb78ff3c7ab3d16b305d6d7182cdae2d3a6e2e","tid":1634820,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644f66ee3c1c1e84fd5f9df77991b14e69662baf","tid":1634820,"uid":2661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:14:58.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"9ad94f62502013c359f826a4d4a6f546b2cc9200","tid":1634820,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /